os-i-herencia-asignacion-coronavirus-en-directo.html|title=Rey Felipe VI. El discurso del monarca por la crisis del coronavirus y reacciones, en directo|date=18 March 2020|website=La Vanguardia|language=es|access-date=18 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abc.es/espana/abci-coronavirus-discurso-felipe-directo-202003182029_directo.html|title=Discurso del Rey Felipe VI por el coronavirus, en directo: \"Este virus no nos vencer\u00e1, nos va a hacer m\u00e1s fuertes como sociedad\"|date=18 March 2020|website=ABC.es|language=es|access-date=18 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n;19 March\n\n[[File:2020-03-14 Desabastiment a Consum Rafelbunyol per compra compulsiva pel COVID-19 02.jpg|thumb|Empty shelves in a [[Consum supermarkets|Consum]] supermarket.]]\n\n* The Canary Islands restrict flights between the peninsula and its islands. Air and sea connections to The Balearic Islands cease due to flight companies stopping all flights.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://elpais.com/economia/2020-03-19/canarias-y-baleares-se-blindan-por-mar-y-aire.html|title=Canarias y Baleares se blindan por mar y aire|last=Marcos|first=Jos\u00e9|date=2020-03-19|website=EL PA\u00cdS|language=es|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n* First reported death of a healthcare worker in the country, a nurse from the Basque Country.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.publico.es/sociedad/crisis-coronavirus-covid-19-cobra-primera-victima-mortal-sanitarios-fallece-enfermera-52-anos-bizkaia.html|title=El Covid-19 se cobra su primera v\u00edctima mortal entre los sanitarios: fallece una enfermera de 52 a\u00f1os en Bizkaia|website=publico.es|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n* Former President of the Community of Madrid and former [[President of the Senate of Spain|President of the Senate]] [[Esperanza Aguirre]] and her husband are hospitalised.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.telemadrid.es/coronavirus-covid-19/Esperanza-Aguirre-marido-hospitalizados-Covid-19-0-2214678554--20200319035455.html|website=telemadrid.es|access-date=