iel|website=eldiario.es|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* [[Ana Pastor (politician)|Ana Pastor]], second vice-president of the Spanish Congress, former [[President of the Congress of Deputies|President of the Congress]] and former [[Ministry of Health (Spain)|Minister of Health]] and [[Ministry of Development (Spain)|of Public Works]], announced she was affected by the coronavirus.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/anapastorjulian/status/1237755582968365057|title=Desde el s\u00e1bado por la tarde que tuve fiebre he permanecido en casa siguiendo las indicaciones m\u00e9dicas. Ayer me dio positivo la prueba del COVID-19 por lo que continuar\u00e9 en mi casa los d\u00edas que me indiquen mis colegas. Yo estoy perfectamente bien sin fiebre ni otros s\u00edntomas.|last=Juli\u00e1n|first=Ana Pastor|date=11 March 2020|website=@anapastorjulian|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* A woman in [[El Vendrell]] becomes the fifth case in the province of Tarragona.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tarragonadigital.com/baix-penedes/nou-cas-coronavirus-tarragona-vendrell-11-marc-2020?fb&fbclid=IwAR1zEjqVG4gES2UGyRM5Mcow81mI8Rij7IbytPfWm_wmAnFhV9YsQbYEdRQ|title=Cinqu\u00e8 cas de coronavirus a Tarragona: una dona del Vendrell infectada|date=11 March 2020|website=Tarragona Digital|language=ca|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Ana Vega, Vox's spokesperson in the [[Corts Valencianes|Valencian Corts]], announces she is positive in COVID-19, becoming the fourth elected politician of the far-right party infected.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/AnaVegaVOX/status/1237777604104654848|title=Desde ayer por la ma\u00f1ana permanezco en casa porque ten\u00eda fiebre. Hoy he dado positivo en la prueba del COVID-19 por lo que cumplir\u00e9 con todas las indicaciones que me han dado las autoridades sanitarias y nuestros profesionales sanitarios.|last=Campos|first=Ana Vega|date=11 March 2020|website=@AnaVegaVOX|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Mini