monia players]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:FC Boto\u0219ani players]]\n[[Category:FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti players]]\n[[Category:Greek expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Greek expatriate sportspeople in Cyprus]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Cyprus]]\n[[Category:Greek expatriate sportspeople in Romania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Romania]]\n[[Category:Association football fullbacks]]\n", "name_user": "Pelmeen10", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aristidis_Soiledis"}
