{"title_page": "Madson (footballer, born 1991)", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Madson\n| image =Univ-Zen16 (8).jpg\n| fullname = Madson Henrique Nascimento Santos\n| height = {{convert|1.78|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1991|5|9}}\n| birth_place = [[Macei\u00f3]], Brazil\n| currentclub = [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| clubnumber = 15\n| position = [[Midfielder#Central midfielder|Central midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 =\n| youthclubs1 =\n| years1 = 2010\n| years2 = 2011\u20132012\n| years3 = 2012\u20132013\n| years4 = 2013\u20132014\n| years5 = 2014\u20132017\n| years6 = 2017\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Centro Sportivo Alagoano|CSA]]\n| clubs2 = [[Paulista Futebol Clube|Paulista]]\n| clubs3 = [[Atl\u00e9tico Clube Goianiense|Atl\u00e9tico Goianiense]]\n| clubs4 = [[FC Vaslui|Vaslui]]\n| clubs5 = [[CS Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]]\n| clubs6 = [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| caps1 = 1\n| caps2 = 15\n| caps3 = 6\n| caps4 = 25\n| caps5 = 60\n| caps6 = 61\n| goals1 = 0\n| goals2 = 0\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 2\n| goals5 = 1\n| goals6 = 1\n| pcupdate = {{date|2020-01-11}}\n}}\n\n'''Madson Henrique Nascimento Santos''' (born 9 May 1991), commonly known as '''Madson''', is a Brazilian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Central midfielder|central midfielder]] for Greek club [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]].\n\n==Club career==\nMadson started his career in his home country, where he played for [[Paulista FC]] and [[Atl\u00e9tico Goianiense]]. In 2013, he was transferred in Europe, to the Romanian squad [[FC Vaslui]].<ref>http://www.vrn.ro/fc-vaslui-isi-intareste-mijlocul</ref><ref>http://www.fcvaslui.info/miscari-de-trupe-la-vaslui/</ref>\n\n===Atromitos===\nOn 8 July 2017 he moved to the [[Greek Superleague]] joining [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]] on a two-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/omades/Atromitos/epishmo-ston-atromhto-o-mantson.4757203.html |title=\u0395\u03c0\u03af\u03c3\u03b7\u03bc\u03bf: \u03a3\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=8 July 2017}}</ref> On 14 October 2017 he scored his first goal with a stunning long shot in a 1-0 home win against [[Asteras Tripoli F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gazzetta.gr/football/article/1148925/atromitos-asteras-tripolis-1-0-vid|title=\u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2 - \u0391\u03c3\u03c4\u03ad\u03c1\u03b1\u03c2 \u03a4\u03c1\u03af\u03c0\u03bf\u03bb\u03b7\u03c2 1-0!|access-date=2017-10-14|language=el}}</ref> As a result of his great performances and the attraction of interest from other teams the administration of the Greek club extended his contract until the summer of 2020.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/omades/Atromitos/ston-atromhto-mexri-to-2020-o-mantson.4940923.html |title=\u03a3\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf \u03bc\u03ad\u03c7\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf 2020 \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=16 November 2017}}</ref> The deal also includes a buy-out clause of \u20ac1,000,000.<ref>[http://www.contra.gr/Soccer/Hellas/Superleague/atromitos/ananewse-o-mantson-mexri-to-2020.4940912.html \u0391\u03bd\u03b1\u03bd\u03ad\u03c9\u03c3\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b5\u03b3\u03ac\u03bb\u03b7 \u03c1\u03ae\u03c4\u03c1\u03b1 \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd \u03bc\u03ad\u03c7\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf 2020] Retrieved 16 November 2017</ref> On 28 November 2017 he scored in an emphatic 4-0 away win against [[Sparta F.C.|Sparti]] for the [[2017-18 Greek Football Cup|Greek Cup]], securing his team's position to the round of 16.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/ellada/GreekCup/ena-hmixrono-htan-arketo-gia-ton-atromhto-4-0-thn-sparth.4959740.html |title=\u0388\u03bd\u03b1 \u03b7\u03bc\u03af\u03c7\u03c1\u03bf\u03bd\u03bf \u03ae\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd \u03b1\u03c1\u03ba\u03b5\u03c4\u03cc \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf, 4-0 \u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u03a3\u03c0\u03ac\u03c1\u03c4\u03b7 |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=28 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|9 July 2019}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Club\n! rowspan=2 | Season\n! colspan=3 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | Continental\n! colspan=2 | Other\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Division\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[FC Vaslui|Vaslui]]\n|[[2013-14 Liga I|2013\u201314]]\n|[[Liga I]]\n|25||2||2||1||\u2013||\u2013||0||0||27||3\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!25!!2!!2!!1!!0!!0!!0!!0!!27!!3\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[CS Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]]\n|[[2014-15 Liga I|2014\u201315]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Liga I]]\n|27||1||2||0||\u2013||\u2013||1||0||30||1\n|-\n|[[2015-16 Liga I|2015\u201316]]\n|25||0||0||0||\u2013||\u2013||1||0||26||0\n|-\n|[[2016-17 Liga I|2016\u201317]]\n|8||0||0||0||\u2013||\u2013||0||0||8||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!60!!1!!2!!0!!0!!0!!2!!0!!64!!1\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n|[[2017-18 Superleague Greece|2017\u201318]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Superleague Greece|Superleague]]\n|26||1||4||1||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013||30||2\n|-\n|[[2018-19 Superleague Greece|2018\u201319]]\n|24||0||5||0||2||0||\u2013||\u2013||31||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!50!!1!!9!!1!!2!!0!!0!!0!!61!!2\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!135!!4!!13!!2!!2!!0!!2!!0!!152!!6\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{soccerway}}\n* {{Sambafoot|7497_madson}}\n\n{{Atromitos squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Madson}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Paulista Futebol Clube players]]\n[[Category:Atl\u00e9tico Clube Goianiense players]]\n[[Category:FC Vaslui players]]\n[[Category:CS Universitatea Craiova players]]\n[[Category:Atromitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:Superleague Greece players]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Romania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Madson\n| image =Univ-Zen16 (8).jpg\n| fullname = Madson Henrique Nascimento Santos\n| height = {{convert|1.78|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1991|5|9}}\n| birth_place = [[Macei\u00f3]], Brazil\n| currentclub = [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| clubnumber = 15\n| position = [[Midfielder#Central midfielder|Central midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 =\n| youthclubs1 =\n| years1 = 2010\n| years2 = 2011\u20132012\n| years3 = 2012\u20132013\n| years4 = 2013\u20132014\n| years5 = 2014\u20132017\n| years6 = 2017\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Centro Sportivo Alagoano|CSA]]\n| clubs2 = [[Paulista Futebol Clube|Paulista]]\n| clubs3 = [[Atl\u00e9tico Clube Goianiense|Atl\u00e9tico Goianiense]]\n| clubs4 = [[FC Vaslui|Vaslui]]\n| clubs5 = [[CS Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]]\n| clubs6 = [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| caps1 = 1\n| caps2 = 15\n| caps3 = 6\n| caps4 = 25\n| caps5 = 60\n| caps6 = 61\n| goals1 = 0\n| goals2 = 0\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 2\n| goals5 = 1\n| goals6 = 1\n| pcupdate = {{date|2020-01-11}}\n}}\n\n'''Madson Henrique Nascimento Santos''' (born 9 May 1991), commonly known as '''Madson''', is a Brazilian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Central midfielder|central midfielder]] for Greek club [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]].\n\n==Club career==\nMadson started his career in his home country, where he played for [[Paulista FC]] and [[Atl\u00e9tico Goianiense]]. In 2013, he was transferred in Europe, to the Romanian squad [[FC Vaslui]].<ref>http://www.vrn.ro/fc-vaslui-isi-intareste-mijlocul</ref><ref>http://www.fcvaslui.info/miscari-de-trupe-la-vaslui/</ref>\n\n===Atromitos===\nOn 8 July 2017 he moved to the [[Greek Superleague]] joining [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]] on a two-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/omades/Atromitos/epishmo-ston-atromhto-o-mantson.4757203.html |title=\u0395\u03c0\u03af\u03c3\u03b7\u03bc\u03bf: \u03a3\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=8 July 2017}}</ref> On 14 October 2017 he scored his first goal with a stunning long shot in a 1-0 home win against [[Asteras Tripoli F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gazzetta.gr/football/article/1148925/atromitos-asteras-tripolis-1-0-vid|title=\u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2 - \u0391\u03c3\u03c4\u03ad\u03c1\u03b1\u03c2 \u03a4\u03c1\u03af\u03c0\u03bf\u03bb\u03b7\u03c2 1-0!|access-date=2017-10-14|language=el}}</ref> As a result of his great performances and the attraction of interest from other teams the administration of the Greek club extended his contract until the summer of 2020.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/omades/Atromitos/ston-atromhto-mexri-to-2020-o-mantson.4940923.html |title=\u03a3\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf \u03bc\u03ad\u03c7\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf 2020 \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=16 November 2017}}</ref> The deal also includes a buy-out clause of \u20ac1,000,000.<ref>[http://www.contra.gr/Soccer/Hellas/Superleague/atromitos/ananewse-o-mantson-mexri-to-2020.4940912.html \u0391\u03bd\u03b1\u03bd\u03ad\u03c9\u03c3\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b5\u03b3\u03ac\u03bb\u03b7 \u03c1\u03ae\u03c4\u03c1\u03b1 \u03bf \u039c\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03c3\u03bf\u03bd \u03bc\u03ad\u03c7\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf 2020] Retrieved 16 November 2017</ref> On 28 November 2017 he scored in an emphatic 4-0 away win against [[Sparta F.C.|Sparti]] for the [[2017-18 Greek Football Cup|Greek Cup]], securing his team's position to the round of 16.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/ellada/GreekCup/ena-hmixrono-htan-arketo-gia-ton-atromhto-4-0-thn-sparth.4959740.html |title=\u0388\u03bd\u03b1 \u03b7\u03bc\u03af\u03c7\u03c1\u03bf\u03bd\u03bf \u03ae\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd \u03b1\u03c1\u03ba\u03b5\u03c4\u03cc \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u0391\u03c4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf, 4-0 \u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u03a3\u03c0\u03ac\u03c1\u03c4\u03b7 |publisher=www.sport24.gr |date=28 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|9 July 2019}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Club\n! rowspan=2 | Season\n! colspan=3 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | Continental\n! colspan=2 | Other\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Division\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n! Apps\n! Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[FC Vaslui|Vaslui]]\n|[[2013-14 Liga I|2013\u201314]]\n|[[Liga I]]\n|25||2||2||1||\u2013||\u2013||0||0||27||3\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!25!!2!!2!!1!!0!!0!!0!!0!!27!!3\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[CS Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]]\n|[[2014-15 Liga I|2014\u201315]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Liga I]]\n|27||1||2||0||\u2013||\u2013||1||0||30||1\n|-\n|[[2015-16 Liga I|2015\u201316]]\n|25||0||0||0||\u2013||\u2013||1||0||26||0\n|-\n|[[2016-17 Liga I|2016\u201317]]\n|8||0||0||0||\u2013||\u2013||0||0||8||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!60!!1!!2!!0!!0!!0!!2!!0!!64!!1\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n|[[2017-18 Superleague Greece|2017\u201318]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Superleague Greece|Superleague]]\n|26||1||4||1||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013||30||2\n|-\n|[[2018-19 Superleague Greece|2018\u201319]]\n|24||0||5||0||2||0||\u2013||\u2013||31||0\n|-\n!